member.remarks:
Updates device details such as name, consumption, or user assignment.
**Authorization**: Requires Admin role
Sample request (update and reassign):
PUT /api/device/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6 { "userId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6", "name": "Updated Device Name", "consumption": "3.2" }
Sample request (unassign device):
PUT /api/device/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6 { "userId": null, "name": "Device Name", "consumption": "3.2" }
